```css
/* 通用样式 */
section.layout div {
	min-height: 100px;
}
.left {
	width: 300px;
	background-color: red;
}
.right {
	width: 300px;
	background-color: blue;
}
.center {
	background-color: yellow;
}
```
### 第一种方案: float
```html
<section class="layout float">
    <div  class="left"></div>
    <div class="right"></div>
    <div class="center">
        <h1>浮动布局解决方案</h1>
    </div>
</section>
```
```css
.float .left {
	float: left;
}
.float .right {
	float: right;
}
```
### 第二种方案: position
```html
<section class="layout position">
	<div class="left"></div>
	<div class="center">
		<h1>绝对定位布局解决方案</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="right"></div>
</section>
```
```css
section.position div {
	position: absolute;
}
section.position .left {
	left: 0;
}
section.position .right {
	right: 0;
}
section.position .center {
	left: 300px;
	right: 300px;
}
```
### 第三种: flexbox
```html
<section class="layout flexbox">
    <div class="left"></div>
    <div class="center">
        <h1>flexbox布局解决方案</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="right"></div>
</section>
```
```css
section.flexbox {
	display: flex;
}
section.flexbox .center {
	flex: 1;
}
```
### 第四种: table
```html
<section class="layout table">
	<div class="left"></div>
	<div class="center">
		<h1>table布局解决方案</h1>
		table布局解决方案
		table布局解决方案
	</div>
	<div class="right"></div>
</section>
```
```css
section.table {
	display: table;
	width: 100%;
	min-height: 100px;
}
section.table>div {
	display: table-cell;
}
```
### 第五种 gird
```html
<section class="layout grid">
	<div class="left"></div>
	<div class="center">
		<h1>grid布局解决方案</h1>
		grid布局解决方案
		grid布局解决方案
	</div>
<div class="right"></div>
</section>
```
```css
section.grid {
	display: grid;
	width: 100%;
	grid-template-areas: 100px;
	grid-template-columns: 300px auto 300px;
}
```
